        "dialogue-before" "29 lines. 130 dependents. Remove me and everything falls. Are you ready?"
        "dialogue-after" "You defeated the root itself. You are the Champion. But the root still stands. It always will."))
    (make-dict
      "name" "Elite Four Hall"
      "description" "The final challenge. Four masters. No healing between battles."
